CPA Qualified Accountant
Confidential Company - ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 13:21:20
Ref. JB3045494
Job Description
You help us deliver the accounting side of our business, provide information and advice to management and participate in all aspects of the operation and development of our business.
You will manage our small inventory.
You will manage accounts in different currencies.
You will provide daily/weekly/monthly reports directly to the manager.
Skills
- Experience with inventory management.
- Experience with QuickBooks.
- Filipino & Female Preferred.
- Experience with Online Shopping Business (preferred)
